    <criterion testable="true">`sprk_analysisaction` row for `summarize-document-for-chat@v1` has `sprk_outputschemajson` populated with a valid draft-07 JSON Schema describing at minimum `summary: string` and `tldr: string[]` (and any other emitted fields).</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Playbook node referencing this action has `destination = chat` per task 031's storage surface.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Migration script is idempotent — second run succeeds without destructive effect; conflict mismatch (existing non-null mismatching schema) FAILS loudly.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">JSON Schema document validates against draft-07 meta-schema.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Regression smoke test: invoking chat `/summarize` continues to render inline as today (widget not yet schema-aware; schema declared but unconsumed).</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">BFF publish-size delta = 0 MB (confirmed in task notes).</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">TASK-INDEX.md updated (032 🔲 → ✅) and `current-task.md` reset.</criterion>
